ent-ArmorHelmetREV = Petrishev Revolutionary helmet
    .desc = A piece of probably stolen from USSP equipment. This one lacks of a famous chin guard of a standart helmet and has a noticibly red hammer and sickle on forehead part.
ent-CCMREVPilotka = Petrishev Revolutionaries pilotka
    .desc = A fancy pilotka with a crossed red sicle and a dark red hammer at the forehead part. You probably shouldn't wear that on public, unless you are... you know.. a heavy armored militant..
ent-CCMHeadCapREVPeaked = Petrishev Revolutionary peaked cap
    .desc = A black officer peaked cap. Used by the officers of Petrishev Revolutionaries.
ent-CCMREVBeret = Petrishev Revolutionaries beret
    .desc = A black beret with a red and dark red colored hammer and sicle. A favorite attribute of Petrishev Revolutionaries veterans.
